OL,5,
OL,6,CG1956FThe BBC TV North Hessary Tor
OL,7,F405-line VHF transmitter is brought
OL,8,Finto service.
OL,9,
OL,10,FBBC documentation states transmissions
OL,11,Ffrom this new permanent mast began on
OL,12,Fthis date. Other sources suggest a
OL,13,Fformal launch on 7th August 1956.
OL,14,
OL,15,FTransmissions from a temporary mast
OL,16,Fbegan in December 1954.
